==============================================================================
ESTIMATORS (re-implementations, NOT vendored)
==============================================================================

The Kraskov-1 mutual information estimator in src/tokenparity/_estimators/
kraskov.py is an Apache-2.0 reimplementation of the method described in:

  Kraskov, A., Stögbauer, H., & Grassberger, P. (2004).
  "Estimating mutual information." Physical Review E, 69(6), 066138.

It is NOT derived from the GPL-licensed NPEET package. No NPEET code was
read or copied during development; reference was made only to the original
2004 paper. CI enforces NPEET-absence: `pip-licenses | grep GPL` must rc=1.
